# Auth and Roles

- Clerk session JWT = the API Bearer token, fetched fresh per request via `auth()` → `getToken()`, server-side only.
- Roles `USER | MANAGER | ADMIN` in Clerk `publicMetadata.role`.
- **ADMIN-only**: `/` (dashboard), `/analytics`, `/staff-users` — everything else MANAGER+.
- MANAGERs land on `/orders`. `USER` has no access.
- Backend 401/403 is the real gate; `proxy.ts` middleware and role-filtered nav are UX only.
